  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You channel an intense burst of chakra into your legs, enveloping them in fiery red energy. Selecting a creature within 60 feet, you instantly teleport to their location and unleash a devastating flurry of kicks.</p><p>Upon teleporting, you make two melee taijutsu attacks against the target. Each attack deals your unarmed damage + 1d8. For every two attacks made, the target must succeed on a Strength saving throw, taking a -2 penalty per successful attack, or be knocked 30 feet in any direction of your choice. A creature can only be knocked upwards once per use of this jutsu.</p><p>If the target fails their save and more attacks remain in this jutsu, you teleport to them again to continue your relentless assault.</p><p><strong>Critical Strike:</strong> If you score a critical hit with this jutsu, instead of doubling the damage dice, the damage dice for that critical attack increase to 1d12s.</p><p><strong>Danger Amplification:</strong> When you teleport to a creature, you may spend 2 Danger Points to attempt an Athletics check contested by the target's passive Perception. On a success, the target is <strong>surprised</strong> for the next two attacks you make against them this turn.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank above B-Rank, increase the chakra cost of this jutsu by 3 and the number of attacks made by +2.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
